Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.90,0:02:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你认输了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.17,0:02:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第四十三话\N剑心练得飞天御剑流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.55,0:02:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼  小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.32,0:02:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.49,0:02:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一个人在这
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.52,0:02:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会不会很寂寞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.66,0:02:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来陪陪我们吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.29,0:02:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.63,0:02:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.83,0:02:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这快死的人管我叫什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.68,0:03:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可怜的小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.92,0:03:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算我们有缘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.79,0:03:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,救了你一命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.33,0:03:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你再恨再气  他们也不会醒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.63,0:03:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我来吧\N免得你一个人孤伶伶的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.10,0:03:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然只有你一个人存活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.94,0:03:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是值得庆幸的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.49,0:03:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么想起以前的往事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.60,0:03:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你还要睡到几点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.80,0:03:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快起来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.77,0:03:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再不起来  我又要回忆往事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.54,0:04:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比方说你在八岁的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.78,0:04:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还会尿床
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.58,0:04:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.55,0:04:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想到你肚子饿的时候\N贪吃的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.76,0:04:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真让人怀念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.79,0:04:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你醒了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.36,0:04:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再睡一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.66,0:04:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,够了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.86,0:04:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飞天御剑流第十三代\N继承者比古清十郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.33,0:04:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,腕力还是一样厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.77,0:04:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是性格还是一样古怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.97,0:04:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.94,0:04:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牛脾气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.04,0:04:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.94,0:04:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孤僻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.34,0:04:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.85,0:04:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在我慢慢想起以前\N你的古怪脾气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.78,0:04:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是狗改不了吃屎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.65,0:04:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来你这个不肖徒弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.05,0:04:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回来就是来找我吵架的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.52,0:04:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.96,0:04:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,世界上像我这样的老师\N已经不多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.36,0:04:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,废话少说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.06,0:04:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再给你一次机会\N不然我就不教你武功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.67,0:05:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要对付老师是要靠一点头脑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.81,0:05:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是最后的机会我要全力以赴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.75,0:05:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.65,0:05:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.84,0:05:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.72,0:05:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你  他只是个孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.53,0:05:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小茜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.46,0:05:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,救救他  救救这个孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.20,0:06:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还要睡  快起来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.48,0:06:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.44,0:06:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也未免太用力了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.68,0:06:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要把我打出脑震荡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.08,0:06:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这个笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.62,0:06:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.19,0:06:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不这样子  你也打不倒我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.82,0:06:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过了十年  你还是这个样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.26,0:06:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遵守诺言  教你武功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.50,0:06:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开始吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.67,0:06:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定要保持绝对的静止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.70,0:06:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果摇动身体  你就没命了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.64,0:06:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首先我先教你剑击的基本招式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.84,0:06:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唐竹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.25,0:06:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,袈裟斩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.65,0:06:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,逆袈裟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.11,0:06:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左刺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.65,0:06:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,右刺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.22,0:06:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左切上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.72,0:06:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,右切上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.19,0:06:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,逆风
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.69,0:07:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有刺突剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.26,0:07:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无论哪一种武功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.66,0:07:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是以此九种招式变化出来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.26,0:07:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以说这九种招式是\N所有武功的基本结构
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.67,0:07:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.38,0:07:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飞天御剑流厉害之处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.82,0:07:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在于能抵抗这九种招式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.68,0:07:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敌人无法防御招架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.99,0:07:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是飞天御剑流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.09,0:07:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“九头龙闪”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.56,0:07:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我最得意的武功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.83,0:07:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的确是让人无法招架的招式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.40,0:07:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要敌人稍有动作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.97,0:07:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马上予以攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.84,0:07:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是“奥义”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.44,0:07:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 在发什么呆  快做做看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.94,0:07:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在就做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.28,0:07:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这个笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.25,0:08:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.02,0:08:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你只看我做\N你怎么可能练得会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.19,0:08:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定要自己实地演练才能领悟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.47,0:08:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道你以前练功\N都是用这种方法吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.33,0:08:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被老师拆穿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.20,0:08:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来你的武功一直都是半吊子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.04,0:08:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.71,0:08:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了就来攻击我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.55,0:08:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的确是不能稍有动作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.25,0:08:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,似乎完全被看透了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.82,0:08:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,九种招式都被掌握住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.60,0:08:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.23,0:08:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飞天御剑流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.93,0:08:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“九头龙闪”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.65,0:09:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该打得到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.66,0:09:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同样是“九头龙闪”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.33,0:09:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么差别那么大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.13,0:09:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道是我的“九头龙闪”有问题吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.60,0:09:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.77,0:09:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的“九头龙闪”没有问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.34,0:09:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是同样的技巧\N不同的使力方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.31,0:09:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,威力当然不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.78,0:09:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乱击术注重的是腕力\N突进术注重的是重量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.58,0:09:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你两者都比我差
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.45,0:09:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以你的九头龙闪\N当然打不过我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.86,0:09:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还是没学会飞天御剑流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.70,0:09:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.90,0:10:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要打败我的“九头龙闪”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.37,0:10:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有一个方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.17,0:10:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是飞天御剑流的精髓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.71,0:10:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是“天翔龙闪”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.45,0:10:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“天翔龙闪”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.75,0:10:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看你那个惊讶的表情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.79,0:10:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.26,0:10:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.39,0:10:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“九头龙闪”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.06,0:10:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我最得意的功夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.96,0:10:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能稍有动作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.80,0:10:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是最大的诀穷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.50,0:10:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“九头龙闪”  是我最得意的武功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.74,0:10:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以前没听人讲过\N“九头龙闪”的厉害吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.38,0:10:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被耍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.42,0:10:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实“九头龙闪”只是教授\N飞天御剑流精髓的试验
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.25,0:10:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通过“九头龙闪”的测试后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.19,0:10:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才能正式教授飞天御剑流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.96,0:10:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以你只要能打败我的“九头龙闪”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.80,0:11:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就学会飞天御剑的精髓了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.30,0:11:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.83,0:11:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想想看“九头龙闪”的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.74,0:11:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就能联想  “天翔龙闪”的轮廓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.14,0:11:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“九头龙闪的样子”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.12,0:11:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然“九头龙闪”是无法防御回避的招式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.59,0:11:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么就只能\N利用出招前攻击了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.13,0:11:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,答对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.66,0:11:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以换句话说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.83,0:11:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“天翔龙闪”就是超神速的武功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.22,0:11:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.47,0:12:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么还不动手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.84,0:12:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还在犹豫什么吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.54,0:12:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你领悟的结果吗\N真是没用的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.08,0:12:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道  可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.22,0:12:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这眼神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.02,0:12:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怕万一我练成了\N会伤害到老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.48,0:12:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.08,0:13:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在你还没练成功前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.45,0:13:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是没有资格讲这种话的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.08,0:13:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给你一个晚上的时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.32,0:13:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让你好好想想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.02,0:13:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你自己要的到底是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.36,0:13:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你欠我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.30,0:13:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你敢以你的命偿还吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.48,0:14:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有没有小孩来过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.31,0:14:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是有这么一个小孩\N像迷路的猫儿来过这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.53,0:14:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,世事难料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.23,0:14:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很多事情都是自己害自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.94,0:14:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是江湖中人常会发生的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.37,0:14:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原本想以飞天御剑流来救人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.61,0:14:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,结果人没救到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.95,0:14:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反而增添许多无辜的生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.02,0:14:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的隐居\N也是想向那些牺牲者谢罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.67,0:15:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还替强盗做坟墓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.01,0:15:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们是人口贩子  不是强盗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.21,0:15:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我父母去年就死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.45,0:15:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.51,0:15:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管是父母或是人口贩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.22,0:15:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死了都一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.75,0:15:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是需要坟墓的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.09,0:15:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那三个石头呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.59,0:15:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是小茜、小花和小樱的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.66,0:15:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们三个人\N被需要钱的家人卖掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.96,0:15:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只见过他们一面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.87,0:15:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是男生  反正我没父母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.94,0:15:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会誓死保护你们的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.91,0:15:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.31,0:15:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我找不到更好的石头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.08,0:15:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只能找到这些  连花也没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.76,0:15:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使成佛了  却不能喝酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.46,0:15:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人生又有什么意义呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.23,0:15:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这点酒表示我一点心意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.83,0:16:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什么名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.37,0:16:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.63,0:16:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我名字太软弱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.94,0:16:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以后你就叫剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.44,0:16:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就跟着我学武功吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.95,0:16:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经十九年了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.75,0:16:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许明天就是今生离别的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.26,0:16:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心什么时候回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.03,0:16:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天就回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.10,0:16:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天你也这么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.20,0:16:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底什么时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.84,0:16:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天一定会回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.51,0:16:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.68,0:16:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.08,0:16:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心请你快回来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.51,0:16:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快回来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.49,0:16:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弥彦  快点进来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.69,0:17:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.72,0:17:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会感冒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.06,0:17:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.33,0:17:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还在下雨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.83,0:17:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绯村一定会练成武功回来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.67,0:17:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.70,0:17:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心只知道牺牲自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.94,0:17:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个人背负那么的重任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.98,0:17:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或许学得武功\N就可以打败志志雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.35,0:17:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但其实剑心的心中还是\N在杀人与不杀人之间矛盾着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.92,0:17:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.39,0:17:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天真是给你添麻烦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.03,0:17:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.30,0:17:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们都是关心剑心的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.50,0:17:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我爷爷也会高兴我这么做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.97,0:17:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我相信剑心回来时\N爷爷就会醒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.17,0:17:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心一定不会背叛小薰的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.54,0:17:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不是那种人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.38,0:17:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.71,0:17:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去看我爷爷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.79,0:18:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈啾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.06,0:18:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好长的旅程\N我们比预计的时间晚到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.03,0:18:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还要过一座山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.20,0:18:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,署长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.54,0:18:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前几天抓到的张十刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.51,0:18:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来和志志雄是同一伙的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.84,0:18:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.75,0:18:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.75,0:18:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.05,0:18:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我相乐左之助终于到京都了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.05,0:19:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还没领略到吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.12,0:19:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.63,0:19:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你就此放弃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.46,0:19:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要如何超越自己\N甚至打败志志雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.63,0:19:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你活着不就是为了战胜痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.94,0:19:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打败孤苦  维护正义吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.71,0:19:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,与其如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.45,0:19:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你倒不如放弃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.92,0:19:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为师的最后任务
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.88,0:19:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是趁现在领你开悟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.46,0:19:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,觉悟吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.64,0:20:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是在怕比古十清郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.11,0:20:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是怕死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.21,0:20:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我怕死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.48,0:20:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在动乱的时候\N我就没有要活下去的理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.62,0:20:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.25,0:20:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有什么好怕死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.22,0:20:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.86,0:20:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这个笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.57,0:20:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是男生  反正我没父母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.77,0:20:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会保护你们的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.81,0:20:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心太  你要坚强的活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.01,0:20:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还小  你不像我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.35,0:20:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以选择自己要走的路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.99,0:20:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.85,0:20:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要坚强活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.99,0:20:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人生就没有白来一趟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.20,0:21:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还是要努力活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.45,0:21:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错  就是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.09,0:21:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杀手总是会一味牺牲自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.16,0:21:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完成任务
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.50,0:21:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以容易轻视自己的生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.63,0:21:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杀手要学会爱惜自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.94,0:21:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才能保护需要被保护的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.27,0:21:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才能持续守护时代的和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.48,0:21:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你成功了  剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.05,0:21:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你已超越自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.52,0:21:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以自己\N将“天翔龙闪”运用自如了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.82,0:22:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你决不会输给志志雄的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.60,0:22:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在你是我的徒弟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.63,0:22:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.10,0:22:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我将为师的使命传交给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.30,0:22:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要为人民的幸福努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.04,0:22:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别再为你的不杀誓言所苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.07,0:22:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而彷徨犹豫了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.79,0:22:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师
